headline: A Look Back at Maintenance and Repair Distributors Stocks’ Q4 Earnings: W.W. Grainger (NYSE:GWW) Vs The Rest Of The Pack
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how maintenance and repair distributors stocks fared in Q4, starting with W.W. Grainger (NYSE:GWW).
